title: ZUCCHINI BREAD OVERNIGHT OATS
directions: Place all ingredients except the walnuts in a container and stir until well combined. Seal with a lid and place in the fridge overnight (or at least a couple hours). Bring out of the fridge in the morning and stir. You'll notice that the oats soak up a lot of the liquid so you may want to add a little more milk before serving. Top oats with walnuts and serve cold.
ingredients: 3/4 cup unsweetened almond or cashew milk
